    },
    {
      "description": "<p><i>Melee Weapon Attack:</i> +4 to hit; reach 5 ft., one target. <i>Hit:</i> 7 (2d4 + 2) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 11 Strength saving throw or have the prone condition.</p>",
